SUMMARY:Follow Your Little Inner Voice of Joy to the New World Dawning Now
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\nYes\, there really
  is a wonderful positive new world dawning now! The old negativity is loud
  and mean these days\, but that’s to be expected as it tries to scare an
 d convince us that there’s no alternative to suffering with it. The “g
 ood” thing about negativity is that it’s so obvious\, once we learn to
  stop believing in its lies. False negative beliefs immediately feel bad a
 nd never work\, including claims that we are weak\, violence is power\, wa
 r brings peace\, and we’ll die if you try to leave the system. Nope\, al
 l sad rubbish\, no matter how many folks get hurt in playing out the dead-
 end scenes. The TRUTH is you are a divine creator consciousness who is wak
 ing up to your own unlimited authority to provide yourself with a better n
 ew reality. Join us this Sunday April 12\, 2026 for a free uplifting talk 
 on how you can ignore the noise to follow your own little inner voice to t
 he joy that is and aways will be yours.\n\nIn all approaches to manifestin
 g – and we will review four – there is one vital skill that starts the
  process of becoming your true self. You need to know what you really need
  and want to do next! If you make the correct choice\, you’ll get into y
 our flow and receive successes easily. The living loving Universe always s
 upports you on your own path to happy ever after. Life is the endless gift
  that you can keep learning to receive. If however you make the incorrect 
 choice for what to do next\, then you’ll be stuck with increasing pain a
 nd suffering. Suffering is endless pain – definitely don’t want that! 
 So it’s often easy to say what outcomes we’re trying to avoid. Far mor
 e challenging is to recognize which path we’re already on when we need t
 o turn around.\n\nWe see this in the world crises today. Few if any folks 
 actually planned to teeter on the brink of disaster. But facing the choice
 s we made to reach this point is tricky and humbling. It’s popular to bl
 ame and wait for someone else to fix our lives for us\, but that’s never
  worked before and never will. Fortunately\, we all have our own little in
 ner voice of joy to guide us home. No kidding\, seriously! I just spontane
 ously laughed when writing that. Silliness and giggles are a good sign\, w
 hen appropriate of course. Children and nature spirits love to laugh with 
 easy joy\, because they’re living so close to the Source. As they say\, 
 angels fly because they take themselves lightly. Jesus loved young people 
 so much that he said\, unless you be like a little child you’ll never en
 ter the kingdom of Heaven.\n\nHaving more fun is not about denials\, callo
 us distractions\, or self-indulgent escapism. So many well-intentioned fol
 ks are bouncing back and forth between addictive emotional extremes withou
 t recognizing who’s really running their show. That would be the negativ
 e ego\, also known as the sociopathic narcissist in psychology\, the fasci
 st in politics\, and the devil in religion. The negative ego is your inner
  critic\, your defensive punisher\, your ruthless invalidator that keeps y
 ou wounded so you cling to other wounded people. And hurt people just keep
  hurting together. The only way to end that sad cycle is to manifest with 
 more of your own true divine power. Your little inner voice of joy is call
 ing you to protect it now\, so that your inherent positive energy will gro
 w to crowd out the weak collapsing negative energy of the futile past. Nee
 d more healing\, don’t feel good enough? No problem! The joys of loving 
 and accepting where you are will set you free with all the miracles you ne
 ed.\n\nFor this meetup\, recall times when you’ve felt truly happy with 
 a carefree joy from life going well for you. How did those times start\, a
 nd how did they end? What strategies work for you to encourage your own de
 light and playful happiness? After check-ins to share and relate\, I’ll 
 explain the spirit-human partnership that is at the heart of every challen
 ge in the world today. Each person is their own Universe that’s learning
  to manifest a great human life. Your little voice of joy is your natural 
 human self who is fine-tuned to feel which way to go for lasting happiness
 . As spiritual consciousness\, you must protect the human being with self-
 loving choices. We’ll look at the tender poignancy of human needs and ho
 w the negative ego cannot fulfill them while the true Source always can. W
 e’ll see how joy is supported in four manifestation approaches\, and lea
 rn the four p’s of self-esteem: passion\, purpose\, positivity\, and pro
 ductivity. We conclude with a guided meditation to invite more playful mag
 ic into the growth and healing that we need with higher friends.\n\nWelcom
 e! Our Inner Selves Mastery spiritual support group is free online every S
 unday 11am-130pm EDT\, with the last 30 minutes for a guided meditation. I
 f you can’t stay you can get the recording. You can signup here for this
  meeting and visit www.signupISM.com for all events\, newsletter\, videos\
 , and more.\n\nBest wishes\,\nCarl Johann Schroeder\nInner Selves Mastery\
 nspiritual teaching and coaching\nquick-links at [www.signupISM.com](http:
 //www.signupISM.com)
